Welcome to the &book-product; Hackers Guide




Welcome to the &book-product; Hackers Guide.  This small book is
designed to aid any person wishing to contribute to &book-product;. If
you are not sure where to begin, take a look at the  page.  This is the best place to
see who is actively involved with the project and provides places to ask
questions. If you know what you are after, then take a look at the
section you are most interested in.



